The package boost-throw-exception is compatible with built-in CMake targets of FindBoost.cmake:

    find_package(Boost REQUIRED COMPONENTS throw_exception)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE Boost::throw_exception)

or the generated cmake configs via:

    find_package(boost_throw_exception REQUIRED CONFIG)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE Boost::throw_exception)
